<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <%- include('layouts/header'); -%>

  <body>
    <%- include('layouts/navbar'); -%>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <header
      class="masthead"
      style="background-image: url('/img/byob-collage-1.jpg');"
    >
      <div class="overlay"></div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 mx-auto">
            <div class="post-heading">
              <h1></h1>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- Post Content -->
    <article>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 mx-auto">
            <div class="col-md-12">
              <div class="card">
                <div class="card-body">
                  <div class="row">
                    <div class="card">
                      <div
                        class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"
                      >
                        <h2 class="card-title font-kalam">
                          Grill Master
                        </h2>
                        <p class="card-text lead">
                          The Grill Master is the penultimate hero of the
                          cookoff. His/her ability to deliver high quality meats
                          to unsuspecting BYOB members is unquestionable.
                        </p>
                        <button
                          id="purchaseTitle-Grill-Master"
                          class="btn btn-custom mt-3"
                          data-title="Grill-Master"
                          >Purchase Title</button
                        >
                      </div>

                       <div
                        class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"
                      >
                        <h2 class="card-title font-kalam">
                          Huck Master
                        </h2>
                        <p class="card-text lead">
                          Huck's Master is the essential father figure you always wanted but never received. His/Her will spend hours playing with their dog children, often times delivering fatal snuggles, before treats.
                        </p>
                        <button
                          id="purchaseTitle-Grill-Master"
                          class="btn btn-custom mt-3"
                          data-title="Huck-Master"
                          >Purchase Title</button
                        >
                      </div>

                       <div
                        class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-center justify-content-center"
                      >
                        <h2 class="card-title font-kalam">
                          Gutter Punk
                        </h2>
                        <p class="card-text lead">
                          Master of savagery and impulsivity, the Gutter Punk is an exceptional anarchist, with studs, boots, and bad odor to boot. He/She will often be found hating the alt-right...click function on keyboards.
                        </p>
                        <button
                          id="purchaseTitle-Grill-Master"
                          class="btn btn-custom mt-3"
                          data-title="Gutter-Punk"
                          >Purchase Title</button
                        >
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="row"></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </article>

    <hr />

    <%- include('layouts/footer'); -%> <%- include('layouts/scripts'); -%>
  </body>
</html>
